{"tid":477234,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"實地考察西九龍地王","createTime":"2017-11-22T23:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T23:55:27.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ee2a915317b5fa88ec18d41fd6dab8dd36965bc8","tid":477234,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T23:55:27.000Z","msg":"繼新鴻基地產以50.6億元投得興華西街酒店地皮之後，隔鄰的大型住宅地皮亦已經公布結果，由信和置業、世茂房地產、會德豐地產、嘉華國際及爪哇控股合組的財團，以172.88億元奪得，金額打破今年2月鴨洲利地王逾168億元紀錄，創出單一地皮的成交新紀錄。<br />\n <br />\n只是這個新發展的區域，很多人都不大了解，曾經到過的人更少，所以筆者到了現場考察，並且參考在區議會和立法會的相關檔案。以下是西九龍地王一帶的規劃：<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xoOfl2fgwMDkwUQ.v.ZnMQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTE0MjtoPTgxMQ--/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/e39b9f52e7a39332e737f67abf8c91f9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FxoOfl2fgwMDkwUQ.v.ZnMQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTE0MjtoPTgxMQ--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fe39b9f52e7a39332e737f67abf8c91f9&h=25558015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西九龍地王1<br />\n<br />\n南昌站有一個出口將會接駁到西九龍地王以及較早前的酒店地盤，現時只能夠通往長沙灣副食品批發市場的閘口，根據規劃圖將會興建行人天橋和升降機塔，並且將修建道路貫穿兩個地盤，以分隔居屋地盤。<br />\n<br />\n而地王地盤中有兩處非建築用地(N.B.A.)，亦有渠務保留用地，所以不會以屏封樓的方式興建，而至少要分作兩大塊。以下各圖是實地拍攝的實景圖，希望能幫助大家了解周遭的情況。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/U.KIp_z6eOEa.3kTaWnNOg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTE5NTtoPTg0Mg--/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/535d9dbb37051831cfd98ac03d2cca64\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FU.KIp_z6eOEa.3kTaWnNOg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTE5NTtoPTg0Mg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F535d9dbb37051831cfd98ac03d2cca64&h=28f3ade1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西九龍地王2<br />\n<br />\n地王前臨海濱長廊，後面是正在興建中的長沙灣副食品批發市場第二期三號和五號地盤，將會作居屋發展。以北隔著西九龍公路是西北九龍海區六號地盤，將作公屋發展和一座八層高的社區文娛康樂設施大樓，以及一座七層高的，而兩者之間又會以升降機塔和行人天橋連接。<br />\n<br />\n所以，當這個社區完全發展之後，除了有港鐵站，有酒店外，更有一樣的社區設施，再加上前臨無敵海景，令到預期的樓價水漲船高，至於最新的實地情況，筆者僅貼上最近的圖片以作參考。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Y2MFKQsuML3JGfGREo_RXA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9NDgw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/e6fc80725b8b47a1968cd19d6c3d8288\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FY2MFKQsuML3JGfGREo_RXA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9NDgw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fe6fc80725b8b47a1968cd19d6c3d8288&h=58c9da44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西九龍地王3<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dIqSVgmPdmIR7RF04X5nvA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9NDgw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/3d91003261a4041ec3db6eeae6266841\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FdIqSVgmPdmIR7RF04X5nvA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9NDgw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F3d91003261a4041ec3db6eeae6266841&h=72797d7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西九龍地王4<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aBpbnlHlVCMklEOaxO7l4A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9NDgw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/ed683165561dc93242fa7cd9dc415deb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FaBpbnlHlVCMklEOaxO7l4A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9NDgw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fed683165561dc93242fa7cd9dc415deb&h=5014aa31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西九龍地王5<br />\n<br />\n脫苦海<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E3%80%90%E8%B6%A3%E9%81%8A%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E3%80%91%E5%AF%A6%E5%9C%B0%E8%80%83%E5%AF%9F%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%9C%B0%E7%8E%8B%EF%BC%88%E8%84%AB%E8%8B%A6%E6%B5%B7%